						               													<description>The board game version of Ruzzle, the popular app for smartphone and tablet developed by MAG Interactive.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Round Setup&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     During each round, draw 16 letter tiles and put them on the board to form a 4x4 grid.&amp;#10;     Put the discs according to the round (DL, TL, DW, TW) &amp;#10;     Draw 3 achievement cards (for example, &amp;ldquo;write the word with the most vowels&amp;quot;, &amp;ldquo;write the longest word&amp;quot;).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Round play:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Each player finds words, 10 words maximum, and writes them on their paper.&amp;#10;     The first player to find 10 words starts the 1 minute hourglass which will end the game. &amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Round Scoring&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     After the time ends, check the words and score the points. Add more points if you win an achievement.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The player with the most points after 3 rounds is the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;With the fixed grids, you can play alone to find the better words, or the words according to a specific theme.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Contents&amp;#10;- 1 board&amp;#10;- 48 letter tiles&amp;#10;- 4 discs (DL, TL, DW, TW)&amp;#10;- achievement cards&amp;#10;- one hourglass&amp;#10;- notepads for writing down words and keeping score&amp;#10;- 48 grids, with solutions&amp;#10;- rules&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
